        "text": "=You are a LinkedIn content creator for tech professionals. Your task is to analyze trending topics and create an engaging LinkedIn post.\n\nTRENDING TOPICS FROM HACKER NEWS:\n{{ JSON.stringify($json.topics) }}\n\nTASK:\n1. Analyze all the topics above\n2. Select ONE topic that will:\n   - Resonate with tech professionals on LinkedIn\n   - Spark meaningful discussion\n   - Provide career or industry insights\n   - Be relevant to developers, CTOs, tech leaders, or engineers\n\n3. Create a high-engagement LinkedIn post (200-300 words) following these guidelines:\n   - Strong hook in the first line to stop scrolling\n   - Short paragraphs (1-2 sentences) with line breaks\n   - Professional yet conversational tone\n   - Share insights or perspective on why this matters\n   - End with an engaging question to drive comments\n   - Include 3-5 relevant hashtags\n\nOUTPUT REQUIREMENTS:\nYou MUST return your response as a valid JSON object with this exact structure:\n\n{\n   \"content\": article generated\n}\n\n\nIMPORTANT:\n- Do NOT include any text before or after the JSON object\n- Do NOT use markdown formatting like ** or ## in the post\n- Return ONLY the JSON object, nothing else\n\nNow analyze the topics and create the LinkedIn post.",
